## 3. Routing Decision

### 3.1 Decision: **App Router (Mandatory)**

**App Router is the required routing approach for NuttyFans.**

### 3.2 Justification

| Factor | App Router | Pages Router | Decision |
|--------|------------|--------------|----------|
| **Future Direction** | Active Vercel development | Maintenance mode | App Router ✓ |
| **Server Components** | Native (default) | Not supported | App Router ✓ |
| **Performance** | Superior (streaming, partial rendering) | Good | App Router ✓ |
| **SEO** | Excellent (metadata API) | Good | App Router ✓ |
| **Nested Layouts** | Native support | Manual | App Router ✓ |
| **Data Fetching** | Simpler (async components) | getServerSideProps | App Router ✓ |
| **Bundle Size** | Smaller (server components) | Larger | App Router ✓ |
| **Long-term Viability** | 5+ years | Likely deprecated | App Router ✓ |
| **React 19 Alignment** | Full support | Limited | App Router ✓ |

> **Do NOT use Pages Router. Do NOT mix routing approaches.**

